Package xxl.core.spatial.geometries.predicates

Useful spatial predicates such as Contains, Overlap, DistanceWithin, etc .

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Contains A predicate that returns true if the first given geometry contains the other one.
Covers A predicate that returns true if geometry0 covers geometry1.
Crosses A predicate that returns true if geometry0 crosses geometry1.
DistanceWithin A predicate that returns true if the distance of the given geometries based on the euclidian-metric is below the specified maximum.
Equals A predicate that returns true if geometry0 equals geometry1 spatially.
Intersects A predicate that returns true if geometry0 intersects geometry1.
Overlaps A predicate that returns true if geometry0 overlaps geometry1.
Relate A predicate that returns true if the spatial relationship specified by the patternMatrix holds.
Touches A predicate that returns true if geometry0 touches geometry1.
TuplePredicate<T> A predicate applicable to arrays.
Within A predicate that returns true if the first given geometry is within the other one.
